<template>
  <el-form :model="login">

    <el-form-item>
      <el-input v-model="login.name" placeholder="用户名">
        <template #prefix>
          <el-icon class="el-input__icon" :size="20"><user/></el-icon>
        </template>
      </el-input>
    </el-form-item>

    <el-form-item>
      <el-input v-model="login.passord" type="password" placeholder="密码" show-password>
        <template #prefix>
          <el-icon class="el-input__icon" :size="20"><lock /></el-icon>
        </template>
      </el-input>
    </el-form-item>


    <el-form-item>
      <el-button type="primary" @click="onSubmit">登录</el-button>
    </el-form-item>
  </el-form>
</template>





<script>
export default {
  created(){
    this.$axios.get('http://localhost:8888/cat/findAll').then((resp)=>{
      console.log(resp)
    })
  }
}
</script>
